    Actions
    This class represents the different values for the possible actions from a given board state.

    Handles all the logic concerning the tic tac toe board.

    This exception is thrown when menace died.
    GameController
    This class handles the overall game logic.
    Logic
    This class handles all the game logic, so for example determining if the game is won.
    Main  
    Matchbox
    This class represents a matchbox.
    MoveException
    This exception is thrown when no move can be made.
    Pair<X,​Y>
    Create a pair, so one object with two objects inside.
    Player
    This class represents a player with a symbol.
    PlayerHuman
    This class represents a human player.
    PlayerMenace
    An implementation of MENACE! This player plays the same as MENACE by using (virtual) matchboxes to pick the move.
    PlayerMinimax
    This player plays by the minimax algorithm without a limit on the depth, thus making a perfect player.
    PlayerNegamax
    This player plays by the negamax algorithm without a limit on the depth, thus making a perfect player.
    PlayerQlearning
    This class represents a player which plays using Q-learning!
    PlayerRandom
    This player makes random moves.
    Symbol
    This enumeration represents the possible values for the cells on the board.
    Transform
    This class can be used to get all the possible transformation on the board and therefore to get all the symmetries of the board.
    Triplet<X,​Y,​Z>
    Create a triplet, so one object with three objects inside.
